L

LINE_OF_DEATH - Static variable in class tbs.TBSGraphics
The LINE_OF_DEATH is the vertical line separating the active elements of the model from the inactive; when a @ModelElement is moved across it, it is either placed in the tree or removed, depending on whether it lands in the active or the inactive portion.
